prompts.frontCover:
A flat 2D illustration of a birthday card front cover, in a beautiful botanical style. In the center, a humorous cartoon depiction of two people. A young East Asian woman, Lao Lao, aged 20-25, is in the foreground, slightly left of center. She has long, straight dark brown hair parted on the side, thin round metal glasses, and a warm, happy smile. She wears a light blue crewneck sweatshirt. Behind her, a young Southeast Asian or East Asian man, Jordan, aged 20-25, with short black textured hair, gives her a big, happy hug from behind. He has a wide, cheerful smile and wears a tan hoodie. The two characters are surrounded by a lush, elegant frame of detailed botanical illustrations: vibrant green ferns, delicate eucalyptus branches, and whimsical watercolor splashes of pastel pink and yellow wildflowers. In the center, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday Lao Lao! You don't look a day over fabulous!"

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
